==Symbols==
The anthem of the International Exhibitions Bureau is the starting part of the 4th Movement of [[Antonín Dvořák|Dvořák]]'s [[Symphony No. 9 (Dvořák)|Symphony No. 9 in E Minor "From the New World"]].{{citation needed|date=May 2016}}

